    "content": "<h3>下一代科技架构</h3><p class='text-white/60 max-w-3xl mb-8'>我们将绝妙的 Web3 协议与坚固的硬件融合，建立无懈可击的安全出口网络。作为 SaaS 提供商，我们为您接管后端所有的架构复杂性。</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12 mb-12\">\n        <div class=\"apple-glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] relative overflow-hidden group border border-white/5 hover:border-[#a88c5a]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(168,140,90,0.15)] bg-black/40\">\n            <!-- Giant Number -->\n            <div class=\"absolute -right-4 -bottom-12 text-[180px] font-black text-white/5 opacity-40 group-hover:text-[#a88c5a]/10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700 pointer-events-none leading-none z-0\">\n                1\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\">\n                <!-- Premium Image -->\n                <div class=\"w-full aspect-video rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden mb-8 border border-white/10 shadow-lg\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/tech-1.png\" alt=\"NXP NTAG (物理防伪锚)\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700\">\n                </div>\n                <!-- Content -->\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#a88c5a]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-inner border border-[#a88c5a]/20\">\n                        <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" class=\"text-[#a88c5a]\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><rect x=\"4\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\"></rect><line x1=\"9\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"4\"></line><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"4\"></line><line x1=\"9\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"23\"></line><line x1=\"15\" y1=\"20\" x2=\"15\" y2=\"23\"></line><line x1=\"20\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"23\" y2=\"9\"></line><line x1=\"20\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"23\" y2=\"14\"></line><line x1=\"1\" y1=\"9\" x2=\"4\" y2=\"9\"></line><line x1=\"1\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"4\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide\">NXP NTAG (物理防伪锚)</h4>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium\">\n                    纯二维码在专业造假面前不堪一击。我们采用物理级安全加密的 NFC 芯片。每次扫描均产生极为复杂的动态变化密码，构建通往数字护照的防伪屏障。\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"apple-glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] relative overflow-hidden group border border-white/5 hover:border-[#a88c5a]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(168,140,90,0.15)] bg-black/40\">\n            <!-- Giant Number -->\n            <div class=\"absolute -right-4 -bottom-12 text-[180px] font-black text-white/5 opacity-40 group-hover:text-[#a88c5a]/10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700 pointer-events-none leading-none z-0\">\n                2\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\">\n                <!-- Premium Image -->\n                <div class=\"w-full aspect-video rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden mb-8 border border-white/10 shadow-lg\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/tech-2.png\" alt=\"Base L2 (安全账本)\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700\">\n                </div>\n                <!-- Content -->\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#a88c5a]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-inner border border-[#a88c5a]/20\">\n                        <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" class=\"text-[#a88c5a]\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><polygon points=\"12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2\"></polygon><polyline points=\"2 17 12 22 22 17\"></polyline><polyline points=\"2 12 12 17 22 12\"></polyline></svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide\">Base L2 (安全账本)</h4>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium\">\n                    让产品身份长存于 Base (以太坊二层网络)。在极低的交易手续费下拥有极高的全网安全扩展性，杜绝服务器遭黑客改写源头的悲剧。\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"apple-glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] relative overflow-hidden group border border-white/5 hover:border-[#a88c5a]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(168,140,90,0.15)] bg-black/40\">\n            <!-- Giant Number -->\n            <div class=\"absolute -right-4 -bottom-12 text-[180px] font-black text-white/5 opacity-40 group-hover:text-[#a88c5a]/10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700 pointer-events-none leading-none z-0\">\n                3\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\">\n                <!-- Premium Image -->\n                <div class=\"w-full aspect-video rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden mb-8 border border-white/10 shadow-lg\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/tech-3.png\" alt=\"版税引擎\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700\">\n                </div>\n                <!-- Content -->\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#a88c5a]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-inner border border-[#a88c5a]/20\">\n                        <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" class=\"text-[#a88c5a]\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path d=\"M21.21 15.89A10 10 0 1 1 8 2.83\"></path><path d=\"M22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2v10z\"></path></svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide\">版税引擎</h4>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium\">\n                    合规不再纯烧钱：智能合约自发执行在产品于欧洲的每一次转售中收取版税的过程。不可修改的代码即规则，实时链上决策分成。\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"apple-glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] relative overflow-hidden group border border-white/5 hover:border-[#a88c5a]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(168,140,90,0.15)] bg-black/40\">\n            <!-- Giant Number -->\n            <div class=\"absolute -right-4 -bottom-12 text-[180px] font-black text-white/5 opacity-40 group-hover:text-[#a88c5a]/10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700 pointer-events-none leading-none z-0\">\n                4\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full\">\n                <!-- Premium Image -->\n                <div class=\"w-full aspect-video rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden mb-8 border border-white/10 shadow-lg\">\n                    <img src=\"/assets/tech-4.png\" alt=\"账户抽象化\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700\">\n                </div>\n                <!-- Content -->\n                <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#a88c5a]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-inner border border-[#a88c5a]/20\">\n                        <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" class=\"text-[#a88c5a]\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"><path d=\"M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2\"></path></svg>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide\">账户抽象化</h4>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium\">\n                    我们采用最新的 ERC-4337 标准。所有的 Gas (矿工费) 统统由我们的后端付款代理出资补偿贴现。以使用传统网上银行直充法币或 USDT 的体验进行企业结算全流程。\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div></div>"
